data.description: Location Location Location!!! Check out this gorgeous home that features a spacious 3BR 2bath floor plan with 1612 sq. ft. of heated living space. This gorgeous home is located right down the road from the up and coming Rogers downtown area, and is also conveniently just a 12min drive from the Walmart amp & Pinnacle Hills entertainment area, for those of you who love the city vibe. Or for you outdoor fans, it is also conveniently just a 10min drive in the other direction to the ever so beautiful Beaver lake.. Hurry in and schedule your showing. Don't miss out on the opportunity of making a piece  NWA a your forever HOME.
